{"tid":2292073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立會補選中涉以福袋誘票投鄭泳舜　李慧琼助理等人被控","createTime":"2020-11-19T08:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T10:46:10.000Z","uid":160592,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"79b3ebd3782f69fb44e0ce2b591a3a9b9301bff4","tid":2292073,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:23:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201119/bkn-20201119144726997-1119_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201119%2Fbkn-20201119144726997-1119_00822_001.html&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopWXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=36353496\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201119/bkn-20201119144726997-1119_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f16ff2f048d000cc3c28a9324b68d71b34442a2a","tid":2292073,"uid":83582,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:24:21.000Z","msg":"助理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ec989db2bc494a983eb8b495ae8c4e5e770435","tid":2292073,"uid":266519,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:25:21.000Z","msg":"老廉喎～<br />\n我以為解散咗添～"},{"pid":"82026b9d5826a9d4d33fea43cbab5ad6e41aee18","tid":2292073,"uid":77717,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:25:37.000Z","msg":"又想洗底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff33e257ef46da842b5088046a331a6053e9862","tid":2292073,"uid":304769,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"63ec989db2bc494a983eb8b495ae8c4e5e770435","tid":2292073,"uid":266519,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:25:21.000Z","msg":"老廉喎～<br />\n我以為解散咗添～"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RtNBXYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRtNBXYn.jpg&h=0fb3ea22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b562188c530192c08e1966aa8063a56c09e0bff2","tid":2292073,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064849a2bdec7c6540c420cef30d976bd9be8c71","tid":2292073,"uid":143230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:44:09.000Z","msg":"講過笑話<br />\n老廉boss 係邊條粉腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12571612da48e26c5b3608018cffe88c7677b67","tid":2292073,"uid":144541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:44:40.000Z","msg":"2018年立法會九龍西補選中，廉政公署調查發現3女1男涉舞弊賄選，其中兩名居民組織義工疑派發「福袋」，以誘賄選民投票給鄭泳舜，同被控一項串謀在選舉中作出舞弊行為罪。另兩名選民涉嫌接受「福袋」以投票予鄭，各被控一項在選舉中作出舞弊行為罪。案件今(19日)在西九龍裁判法院開審。<br />\n4名被告分別為深水埗海麗邨居民組織「海麗之友社」義工鄧奕梅(42歲)及王維霞(52歲)，以及海麗邨居民陳惠娟及李謀(均50歲)。<br />\n控方開案陳詞指，4名被告均為海麗邨居民，其中第二被告於2017年3月12日至翌年8月31日期間，是立法會議員李慧琼的兼職議員助理。<br />\n2018年3月4日，次被告要求首被告收集海麗邨居民的個人資料，包括姓名、電話號碼和地址，首被告最終將包括第三和四被告等10人的資料交給次被告，而除了第四被告和另一人外，其他人士均為登記選民。<br />\n到3月11日，首被告再提醒第三和四被告等人投票給鄭泳舜，第三被告最終在補選中投票，第四被告當時回覆指正前往票站投票，但因他是在登記期限後才成為選民，故最終不獲准在該票站投票，但他仍告知首被告已投票給鄭泳舜。<br />\n控方表示將傳召多名街外證人，講述首兩名被告如何藉送禮邀約他們投票給指定的人，並會將各人的WhatsApp紀錄呈堂。辯方則爭議有關短訊紀錄是否可足以讓法庭推論出有舞弊情況 。"},{"pid":"bc9d465a662f50b952beae5a42e58ad212ceacbc","tid":2292073,"uid":67454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"064849a2bdec7c6540c420cef30d976bd9be8c71","tid":2292073,"uid":143230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:44:09.000Z","msg":"講過笑話<br />\n老廉boss 係邊條粉腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:46:48.000Z","msg":"柒婆唔妥保皇黨好耐<br />\n趕走哂泛民，跟住咪清算condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7d4007df5efe1d31073eea6998707689a78344","tid":2292073,"uid":33939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:50:49.000Z","msg":"助理做替死鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw，助理何來有錢買福袋派？"},{"pid":"2dbc7d32175dca2d1e493eed9edc5b94deec3bc3","tid":2292073,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ff33e257ef46da842b5088046a331a6053e9862","tid":2292073,"uid":304769,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"63ec989db2bc494a983eb8b495ae8c4e5e770435","tid":2292073,"uid":266519,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:25:21.000Z","msg":"老廉喎～<br />\n我以為解散咗添～"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RtNBXYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRtNBXYn.jpg&h=0fb3ea22&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:56:24.000Z","msg":"門口長期有地產廣告 , 感覺真係好 off <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9558f8d1ac55318fa6477d7f49e917cbafafecb","tid":2292073,"uid":210755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T08:58:06.000Z","msg":"次次都影哂片民建聯啲人捉掌心雷公公婆婆去投票 ，啲婆婆都話唔識 啲人叫佢投就投<br />\n咁都唔拉"},{"pid":"ac4121d044b34359a6d20a33e84f7d175417be00","tid":2292073,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T10:46:10.000Z","msg":"律政司：唔告<br />\n党安：ICAC違反党安法"}]}